{"tid":649520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孩童朝南京大屠殺紀念碑丟石　家長全程旁觀不制止","createTime":"2018-05-01T15:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T19:16:52.000Z","uid":179810,"like":95,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c6264edd95675ada7642752bb7805e80d5b9fab1","tid":649520,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180501/photo/bkncn-20180501184231472-0501_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180501221918\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180501%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180501184231472-0501_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180501221918&h=b7f436ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180501/photo/bkncn-20180501184231472-0501_05011_001_02p.jpg?20180501221918\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180501%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180501184231472-0501_05011_001_02p.jpg%3F20180501221918&h=efea9fd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n江蘇南京市政府為悼念南京大屠殺的死難者，1985年在當地建立侵華日軍南京大屠殺遇難同胞紀念館，以供後人了解歷史。惟有南京市民周日（29日）到訪該址時，發現有多名孩童正向「災難之牆」丟石，他們的家長竟然全程旁觀，未有出手制止。 <br />\n<br />\n該名爆料網民指，當日涉事的孩子站在「災難之牆」前方的水池處，不斷拿起石頭對準紀念碑砸過起，又在水池玩起打水漂。據稱，該批孩子是跟隨家長來，但直到網民一行人離開，都未見有人叫停孩子的行為，埸館保安亦從未現身。 <br />\n<br />\n事發短片在網上曝光後，引起公憤。紀念館事後亦在官方微博發文，表示由於當日為五一假期，有6.2萬人到訪，故館方應接不暇。惟該館亦承認保安巡查存在疏漏，即日起會安排固定保安人員在「災難之牆」值守，以防類似事件再發生。"},{"pid":"dfdd619a3989abf1ae6d5719f7275dba0fe4104f","tid":649520,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"反了反了"},{"pid":"0f2cc1b45bf7f84679cbe97595a8fca7c8c11712","tid":649520,"uid":83582,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"個細路認為南京大屠殺唔係災難, 所以掟石反對"},{"pid":"16a111923c9eabdf091e2b39682015d19cfefb26","tid":649520,"uid":89514,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:51:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"211e306fc4f7f954b8eed51a91dca71a339b630c","tid":649520,"uid":67302,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:51:34.000Z","msg":"支那童今次做得好"},{"pid":"4214b9710dac2ee3599a8fe0bb8deb5c5f055e60","tid":649520,"uid":90,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:53:54.000Z","msg":"沒事沒事，他只是個孩子<br />\n小孩子就這樣，這樣才健康"},{"pid":"d6fa9e1126e48604a9b9be43754e9e902bcc64b1","tid":649520,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:54:09.000Z","msg":"老衲啲仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877a30f938c964fabd36f2b8d9fa69fd4b33c1c7","tid":649520,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:54:50.000Z","msg":"厉害了, 我的(蝗)蟲"},{"pid":"50d65aa29ffecd82d4a564e2864d2e8d6b9c0605","tid":649520,"uid":28913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"殺得唔夠多"},{"pid":"bf697346d0b2cbedadc798444b07d934193896bd","tid":649520,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:59:22.000Z","msg":"一定係日本人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b73bd09957ec35fbc64dd5a98f6ca4992bc7d99","tid":649520,"uid":60831,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T16:01:26.000Z","msg":"他只是個孩子啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f585b7fe1cf1d38a7c8c4bf58311862311dd100","tid":649520,"uid":157182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T16:01:54.000Z","msg":"扔穿牆，與日本和好！"},{"pid":"df0e2a6c08cc2178a0edf86980189ccca41e5dee","tid":649520,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"0負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5096b07ced19a4a9e129c8d352e58d2af39a5401","tid":649520,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-